                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 120.) The prisoners were given to me—I went to Dennis, and got the boots—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18450106-name-267" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18450106-name-267" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
